panels.description: Como descreve a mobilidade de idosos e pessoas com dificuldade de locomoção em sua casa?

ANDA SEM SOPORTE MAS COM DIFICULDADE.text: ANDA SEM SUPORTE MAS COM DIFICULDADE

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  question_1 as resposta,
  COUNT(*) AS quantidade
FROM forms
WHERE
  question_1 IS NOT NULL AND
  $__timeFilter(date) 
GROUP BY question_1
ORDER BY quantidade DESC

panels.title: Questão 2

panels.description: Existe alguma deficiência sensorial em algum habitante da sua casa?

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  question_3 as resposta,
  coord_s as lat,
  coord_w as lng
  -- COUNT(*) as valor
FROM forms
WHERE
  question_3 IS NOT NULL
  AND (question_3 <> 'SEM INFORMAÇÃO' AND question_3 <> 'NÃO')
  AND $__timeFilter(date) 
GROUP BY question_3, lat, lng
-- ORDER BY valor DESC

panels.title: Questão 6

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  sex as sexo,
  COUNT(*) as quantidade
FROM residents
JOIN forms ON residents.form_id = forms.id
WHERE
  sex IS NOT NULL AND
  sex in ('M', 'F') AND
  $__timeFilter(date) 
GROUP BY sex
ORDER BY quantidade DESC

SELECT
  COUNT(*) as quantidade,
  CONCAT(10*FLOOR(age/10), ' - ', 10*FLOOR(age/10)+9) AS bucket_idades -- magia negra, não questione # https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6669730/sql-query-that-groups-different-items-into-buckets
FROM residents
JOIN forms ON residents.form_id = forms.id
WHERE
  age IS NOT NULL AND
  $__timeFilter(date)
GROUP BY bucket_idades
ORDER BY bucket_idades

SELECT
  CASE
      WHEN education IN ('ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL', 'FUNDAMENTAL') THEN 'ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL'
      ELSE education
  END AS parsed_education,
  COUNT(*) as quantidade
FROM residents
JOIN forms ON residents.form_id = forms.id
WHERE
  education IN ('MÉDIO', 'FUNDAMENTAL', 'ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL', 'ENSINO MÉDIO', 'NENHUMA', 'FACULDADE') AND
  $__timeFilter(date)
GROUP BY parsed_education
ORDER BY quantidade DESC
